### Register Go Function
POST http://localhost:8089/api/v1/lambda/functions
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwZSI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmN2I4Y2FkZC05MmNiLTQ4MzAtYTU2NS1hMWM5MDM1OTdmYzYiLCJpYXQiOjE3MTE5OTY4MDB9.
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

hello-gow
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

lambda
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"

golang:1.22-alpine
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="execution.kind"

binary
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resources.cpu"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resources.memory"

128
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="handler"
Content-Type: application/octet-stream

< ./handler
--boundary--

### Invoke Go Function
POST http://localhost:8089/api/v1/lambda/invoke
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwZSI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmN2I4Y2FkZC05MmNiLTQ4MzAtYTU2NS1hMWM5MDM1OTdmYzYiLCJpYXQiOjE3MTE5OTY4MDB9.
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "hello-gow",
  "payload": {
    "name": "World"
  }
}

### Register Node.js Function
POST http://localhost:8089/api/v1/lambda/functions
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwZSI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmN2I4Y2FkZC05MmNiLTQ4MzAtYTU2NS1hMWM5MDM1OTdmYzYiLCJpYXQiOjE3MTE5OTY4MDB9.
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=boundary

--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="name"

hello-node
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="type"

lambda
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"

node:18-alpine
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="execution.kind"

node
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resources.cpu"

1
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="resources.memory"

128
--boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="app.js"
Content-Type: application/javascript

< ./app.js
--boundary--

### Invoke Node.js Function
POST http://localhost:8089/api/v1/lambda/invoke
Authorization: Bearer eyJhbGciOiJub25lIiwidHlwZSI6IkpXVCJ9.eyJ1c2VySWQiOiJmN2I4Y2FkZC05MmNiLTQ4MzAtYTU2NS1hMWM5MDM1OTdmYzYiLCJpYXQiOjE3MTE5OTY4MDB9.
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "hello-node",
    "payload": {
        "message": "Hello from Node"
    }
}

